{"tid":263944,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【4月新番】不正經的魔術講師與禁忌教典【第 9 話】","createTime":"2017-05-30T12:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T16:23:15.000Z","uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cce21529c3e253b584a4c129d23933085a982746","tid":263944,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rokuaka.jp/img/bg2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frokuaka.jp%2Fimg%2Fbg2.jpg&h=a15f1233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不正經的魔術講師與禁忌教典<br />\nロクでなし魔術講師と禁忌教典<br />\nRokudenashi Majutsu Koushi to Akashic Records<br />\n<br />\n賴在別人家裡、一年過著無職生活的 葛倫&middot;雷達斯，在家主的強迫下到 阿爾扎諾帝國帝國魔術學院擔任兼職講師。但他假自習之名行打瞌睡之實，就算難得站上了講台，他也是直接把課本釘在黑板上。就在想早點辭職的心態下，被學生 西絲蒂娜&middot;席貝爾提出了決鬥。結果令人遺憾地，葛倫以懸殊的差距吞下了敗戰&hellip;&hellip;然而與政府敵對的魔術結社「天之智慧研究會」襲擊了學院，葛倫也被捲進了一連串的紛爭之中。<br />\n<br />\nPV2<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6lYVx8lQGSw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6lYVx8lQGSw&d=e3vSqkJZa08LwYwIKWn%2FM57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=96efc3ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6lYVx8lQGSw</a><br />\n<br />\nPV3<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nzlblisGahI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnzlblisGahI&d=e3vSqkJZa08LwYwIKWn%2FM57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=19c98f67\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nzlblisGahI</a><br />\n<br />\nOP PREVIEW<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pfWKAxeySvE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpfWKAxeySvE&d=e3vSqkJZa08LwYwIKWn%2FM57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=53f7be19\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pfWKAxeySvE</a><br />\n<br />\nED PREVIEW<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1vfnFjr4rd8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1vfnFjr4rd8&d=e3vSqkJZa08